headline: Why TowneBank (TOWN) Is Up 5.4% After Raymond James Reaffirms Buy On Revenue Growth – And What's Next
summary: In early January 2026, Raymond James reaffirmed its Buy rating on TowneBank after the regional lender reported year-over-year revenue growth in its latest earnings release. This combination of analyst endorsement and improving top-line performance has drawn fresh attention to how TowneBank’s fundamentals are perceived by the market.
